 JOHANNESBURG -Â The ANC in Nkangala Region has sent condolences following the death of the Mayor of Emalahleni. Linah Malatjie died in a car crash on Sunday night. Her husband, who was in the car, was also killed. Their car collided with another vehicle between KwaMhlanga and Emalahleni. The ANC in the region says it will remember Malatjie for her commitment as a public servant and struggle activist. Statement on Passing of Emalahleni Executive Mayor by eNCA.com on Scribd 